==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# The act of [[objecting]].
# A [[statement]] expressing [[opposition]], or a [[reason]] or [[cause]] for expressing opposition.
# A official protest raised in a [[court of law]] during a [[legal trial]] over a violation of the rules of the court by the opposing party.

